Rewrapped - Season 1, Episode 3




SpaghettiOMG

The Rewrapped kitchen travels down memory lane with SpaghettiOs with Meatballs and goes from "uh-oh" to "oh yeah" when one contestant rolls out dough from scratch. In the Innovate Challenge, the contestants take this iconic canned pasta on a world tour with their international dishes. From Asian Lettuce Wraps to SpaghettiOs Stuffed Pierogies, you won't believe your eyes on this SpaghettiOs showdown!




Original Air Date: 28-Apr-2014
